						<summary>

						<p>A broken slab.</p>						

						<p>Rim of a bowl made of greyschist. Impression from the Director. Findspot: Gandhāra West Pakistan.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary and damaged record refers to a grant for worship and offerings to the god Mallikārjuna. There is a mention of the place Bāḍa.</p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 11th century A.D.</p>						

